Enum Region

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Region>
      • net.dv8tion.jda.core.Region
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Region>

    public enum Region
extends java.lang.Enum<Region>
    Represents the Regions used for Audio connections.
    This is used by Guild to where the server that hosts the Guild is located.
